2026-05-18T00:14:02.9491341Z [36;1m      failures <- result[result$failed + result$warning > 0, ][0m
2026-05-18T00:14:02.9491656Z [36;1m      print(failures)[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:02.9491883Z [36;1m      if (nrow(failures) > 0) {[0m
