2026-05-18T00:14:02.9492786Z [36;1m        print(failures$result)[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:02.9493033Z [36;1m        testthat::snapshot_accept()[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:02.9493353Z [36;1m        writeLines("changed=true", Sys.getenv("GITHUB_OUTPUT"))[0m
2026-05-18T00:14:02.9493666Z [36;1m      } else {[0m
